data.description: This stunning property is nestled on 1.5 acres in the New West Lake Subdivision.  Country living, close to the conveniences of town; just 12 miles from Calallen and 7 miles from Orange Grove. With beautiful, mature trees and an oversized back porch, you can enjoy beautiful sunsets with extraordinary views.  Interior features include a large master suite, a woodburning fireplace, an open floor plan, a built-in desk area, new window coverings, and plenty of room for entertaining. Outside shed is perfect for storage or 4H projects. Recently replaced water well pump, septic tank, and water heater.
